            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              <p class="text-base leading-6 text-green-800">
                We agree with this short description on <%= link_to 'Wikipedia', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diablo_Valley', target: :blank, class: "underline hover:text-green-900" %>, which places the "Diablo Valley" west/northwest of Mount Diablo. It includes the cities north of Highway 24 and along the 680 artery.
              </p>
            </dd>
