          <div class="mt-12">
            <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-green-900">
              How did the DVTI come about?
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              <p class="text-base leading-6 text-green-800">
                The DVTI began when a member of the Business Administration Department Advisory Board at Diablo Valley College asked an intriguing question: Why aren't there more tech companies based in the Diablo Valley? A committee was formed to look into it, and that committee became the DVTI.
              </p>
            </dd>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <dt class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-green-900">
              Is the DVTI funded by Diablo Valley College (DVC)?
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2">
              <p class="text-base leading-6 text-green-800">
                Yes and no. It is supported by DVC but funding comes from state and federal grants for workforce development. Since the interests of the DVTI and DVC are so well-aligned, it has been a natural partnership, but DVTI does not take funding away from other DVC programs.
              </p>
            </dd>
          </div>
        </div>
